观看 The Killers 邀请粉丝在 2023 年雷丁比赛中与他们一起打鼓https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-killers-invite-fan-to-play-drums-with-them-at-reading-2023-3489069?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-杀手邀请粉丝在 2023 年阅读时与他们一起打鼓Erica CampbellSat, 26 Aug 2023 23:12:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsReading & Leeds FestivalIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3489069 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杀手们" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队要求鼓手加快节奏，说“可卡因比大麻更多”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-killers-invite-fan-to-play-drums-with-them-at-reading-2023-3489069">《Watch The Killers》邀请粉丝在雷丁 2023 上与他们一起打鼓的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杀手们" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Drummer-Chris-Phelps-Credit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-festival-2023">2023 年雷丁节</a>演出期间，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">杀手乐队</a>邀请了一名粉丝上台与他们一起打鼓。观看下面的片段。</p><ul><li style="list-style-type: none;"><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/reading-festival-2023-liveblog-all-of-the-weekends-action-as-it-happens-3488589" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/reading-festival-2023-liveblog-all-of-the-weekends-action-as-it-happens-3488589&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1693121657062000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1nsy7zD9s4KrJa-F4NAcj-">2023 年读书节直播博客：周末发生的所有活动</a></strong></li></ul></li></ul><p>这位名叫奥兹的粉丝举着牌子，要求与他们一起打鼓，但这在《杀手》片场并没有成为传统。</p><p> “我们有一个很大的规定，”主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brandon-flowers">布兰登·弗劳尔斯</a>在让奥兹上台之前问他。 “让我看看你的脸？我喜欢你的标志，但你来自哪里？你来自英国。让孩子起来吧。”根据弗劳尔斯的说法，鼓手来自“巴斯郊外”。奥兹穿上克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多的球衣，让乐队的节奏保持较慢，而弗劳尔斯则敦促他加快速度。</p><p> “走快点，”弗劳尔斯开玩笑说，“可卡因比大麻还多”。观众们对这一刻表示认可，在奥兹离开舞台时高喊着他的名字。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CwbPDU5tZLl/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; 